Solr Quickstart Maven Archetype

This archetype is supposed to automate the creation of a project that uses Apache Solr.
It can also provide an acceptance tests framework using EasyB


-- HOW DOES IT WORKS:

* checkout the project
* mvn clean install

* mvn archetype:generate -DarchetypeGroupId=com.sourcesense.solr -DarchetypeArtifactId=solr-quickstart -DarchetypeVersion=0.3-SNAPSHOT


THIS COMMIT IS A TEST